configurationImportHistoryDTO Data Type

Contains all of the information about a previous configuration import.

Namespace
(Default)
Properties
name data type type namespace min/max occurs description
accept_date dateTime element 0/1  
accept_user justUserDTO element 0/1  
messages configurationImportMessageDTO element 0/unbounded The informational messages generated when the configuration was initially imported. Contains detailed messages about the import.
reject_date dateTime element 0/1  
reject_user justUserDTO element 0/1  
status string element 0/1 The status of the import. Currently the possible values are INVALID, PENDING, ACCEPTED, REJECTED, IMPORT_ERROR.
Properties inherited from configurationHistoryDTO
dateTime element 0/1 The date that the import/export was created.
int element 1/1 The internal ID of the import/export
justUserDTO element 0/1 The user that performed the import/export.
